                            <h4>How can I earn SupportPoints?</h4>
				<p>
				We'll occasionally prompt you to give someone a small "push" who really needs it.
	With the push one of their buttons, we'll send them some motivation, and you'll earn 5 "SupportPoints". 
	If they succeed within 48 hours, you'll earn an additional 10 "SupportPoints"!
				</p>

                            <h4>What can I do with my SupportPoints?</h4>                            
					<p>
                                        Every 100 SupportPoints earns you a free $10 Premium Membership for either you or a friend!
				        </p>


                            <h4>I've got 100 or more SupportPoints. How can I "cash them in"?</h4>
                                        <p>
Send an email to support@habitforge.com and specify what you'd prefer. You can:
<br>1. Get a 1 year Premium Membership
<br>2. Extend a current Premium Membership by 1 year
<br>3. Give a Premium Membership to a friend (simply include their email address in your email to support)
                                        </p>


